{"tid":1556002,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"[極緊急] 求幫P牌推  有關 2019-08-13 帳號保安問題","createTime":"2019-09-09T14:32:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T11:12:42.000Z","uid":320316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"59df7596cfd7902dc19f57876a992f52c093d756","tid":1556002,"uid":320316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:32:25.000Z","msg":"幾經辛苦終於申請到個帳號入黎開post<br />\n8月個陣 帳號突然之間比人改左密碼入唔到<br />\n隨後就見到站務台講連登大專email被黑客入侵<br />\n有個傻仔比人hack左 果個就係我 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/25163\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/25163</a> ( #25163 琳寶堅尼) <br />\n連仔當時好迅速咁處理左被hack帳號<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">(掌握所有被盜的帳戶及作暫時禁言處理，受影響用戶將會收到通知，屆時請立即以電郵方式與我們聯絡以取回帳號。)</span></span></strong><br />\n但由於我個isp電郵係當年畢業之後就再登入唔到 所以一直都拎唔番個ac<br />\n所以懇求大家幫幫手推推比連仔睇到 拎番個帳號<br />\n<br />\n出親去有時想上連登通知現場情況  有事想開post都做唔到 而且p牌又極多限制 <br />\n求連仔幫幫手 需要證明我都可以提出 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命 </span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb8cc7b825bf27e4cc77e493f7b3ebfe474b0794","tid":1556002,"uid":320316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:34:55.000Z","msg":"呢排冇帳號 加密既野一啲都睇唔到阿陰公 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又推唔到post 有冇好心人打救下我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後一個post去機場問人借止汗劑之後就再用唔到啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be00efebcaaa2c4464272e725ce438b011d369dc","tid":1556002,"uid":320316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:44:57.000Z","msg":"救命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b62762d5f46d06999190b1cdb2c6fcdcd9ede12f","tid":1556002,"uid":320316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:16:01.000Z","msg":"有矛好心人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"614169bb1e0c6bb9c3f7187f21cc06d401c6eaf1","tid":1556002,"uid":157766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:27:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114dd7258144761d9807c03c34ce85584203afea","tid":1556002,"uid":320316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:44:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c967e51e4b30799d840cd544cf5a292ab3585595","tid":1556002,"uid":320316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:56:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"387fa2ad902e5d58962b0d320ecc322fb257dbf2","tid":1556002,"uid":52296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T00:47:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022485f5e33cff00bb21df092fd870cb4199d104","tid":1556002,"uid":320316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T11:12:42.000Z","msg":"連仔help <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}